<li id="c1">
  <div class="cx" id="cx49239771">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">I want my Daffy Duck vote to count, too, </span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1183112/49239771#c1?mode=alone;showrate=1#c1">3+ / 0-</a>)</span>
