    </dd>
  
</dl></div>

  

  <div class="ct">
  
<p>but I don't expect the electoral college to follow suit.</p>
<p>The principle ought to be simple enough even for a Republican:<br /></p>
<blockquote><strong>ONE VOTE = ONE VOTE</strong></blockquote>

  </div>
  <div class="cf">
