<div class="crs"><dl>
  <dt>Recommended by:</dt><dd>
  <a href="/user/uid:113074">HappyinNM</a>, <a href="/user/uid:1621">DaddyO</a>, <a href="/user/uid:52151">phree</a>, <a href="/user/uid:57095">Overseas</a>
    </dd>
  
</dl></div>

  

  <div class="ct">
  
<p>Democrats in Texas are used to voting for no reason. &nbsp;It would drive up the voter participation in Texas if we knew that our vote would actually mean something, instead of being gerrymandered out by a hypermajority of Republicans.</p>

  </div>
